223114028/http://news.mtime.com/2017/06/23/1570648.html |archive-date=2017-12-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Matt Pressberg |title=China Now Has More Movie Screens Than US |url=https://www.thewrap.com/china-now-movie-screens-us/ |accessdate=2020-03-11 |work=TheWrap |date=2017-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008174550/https://www.thewrap.com/china-now-movie-screens-us/ |archive-date=2019-10-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年度的票房表現受到[[2019冠狀病毒病中國大陸反應與影響#电影业|2019冠状病毒病疫情的影響]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=Nancy Tartaglione |title=2020 Worldwide Box Office Slumps 71% To 12.4B Amid Covid Impact: Strength Of International, Piracy Concerns & Hope Dominate 2021 Chatter – Global Studio Rankings Chart |url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/hollywood-movie-studio-global-rankings-2020-global-international-box-office-analysis-2021-outlook-1234665561/ |accessdate=2021-01-21 |work=Deadline |date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2022-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306031340/https://deadline.com/2021/01/hollywood-movie-studio-global-rankings-2020-global-international-box-office-analysis-2021-outlook-1234665561/ }}</ref>；同年10月，超越[[美国电影|美國]]成為[[全球歷年電影票房|全球第一大電影市場]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=Nancy Tartaglione |title=China Kicks Off 2021 With Record New Year’s Day Box Office As Market Ends 2020 At No. 1 Globally |url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/china-new-year-day-record-2021-a-little-red-flower-overtakes-north-america-2020-box-office-1234664033/ |accessdate=2021-01-21 |work=Deadline |date=2021-01-03 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113171819/https://deadline.com/2021/01/china-new-year-day-record-2021-a-little-red-flower-overtakes-north-america-2020-box-office-1234664033/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

